                    <h2 class="py-4">About FLOAT/THERE</h2>
                    <h5>We're changing the art of packing.</h5>
                    <p class="pt-3">Ever been excited about a vacation but dreaded planning outfits
                        and packing for it? Us too. We found ourselves wanting (or needing) 
                        new clothes and spending money shopping for trips, only to wear those items 
                        once or twice and then never again. Sometimes we would run out of room in 
                        our suitcase or weekend bag. Or even worse, at times our online orders 
                        wouldn't even arrive in time to pack.
                    </p>
                    <p>So we decided to start FLOAT/THERE, determined to help travelers look and 
